    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/1672b00994c39fdfbcc6d2acdebbb08d.poster.avif?t=1761644137\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/1672b00994c39fdfbcc6d2acdebbb08d.webm?t=1761644137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/1672b00994c39fdfbcc6d2acdebbb08d.mp4?t=1761644137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME ABOARD!</h2></h2>TRIP is a short narrative first person game, set on a strange and surreal train.<br>Explore and learn more about its unique passengers and unravel all the mysteries !<br>Or feel free to take a seat and watch the scenery roll by, in this colorful retro aesthetic world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/bcc0d2a21b6f588ae683a4c6c34d23a5.poster.avif?t=1761644137\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/bcc0d2a21b6f588ae683a4c6c34d23a5.webm?t=1761644137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/bcc0d2a21b6f588ae683a4c6c34d23a5.mp4?t=1761644137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>At start funny, you'll slowly discover that the game hides mysterious and dark secrets !<br>Will you dare to go to the end of this fabulous trip?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/4f3761b33c4f3b92dcb56399b92081cb.poster.avif?t=1761644137\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/4f3761b33c4f3b92dcb56399b92081cb.webm?t=1761644137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/4f3761b33c4f3b92dcb56399b92081cb.mp4?t=1761644137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY FEATURES</h2></h2>Walk and talk to the various characters.<br>Explore the environment.<br>Interact with some objects (like sitting down on a seat or opening a door)<br>Investigate and understand how to progress in the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/7fd43dfa4126404dbede4cfbdf941760.poster.avif?t=1761644137\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/7fd43dfa4126404dbede4cfbdf941760.webm?t=1761644137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778150/extras/7fd43dfa4126404dbede4cfbdf941760.mp4?t=1761644137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play with mouse and keyboard.<br>The game is still in development, I am aiming for an 1 hour long gameplay experience.<br>Add it to your wishlist and stay tuned !",
